atlas.entity.view

Class CategoryView

  • java.lang.Object
    • atlas.entity.view.CategoryView

  • public class CategoryView
extends Object
    Represents a localized view of a category. Basically a set of attributes of CategoryInfo and its related Category. Namely, attributes useful for generating category lists and links (ID, localized name, latin name, number of pages).
    Author:
    Michal Smrha
    See Also:
    Category, CategoryInfo
